text: Desmiphora elegantula is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by White in 1855. It is known from Brazil, Venezuela and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora elegantula. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1855
